`8Keywords``   : Ray_Of_Truth
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'ray of truth' <target>

 Ray of truth opens a portal to the planes of positive energy, bringing forth a
beam of light of sufficient purity to harm or annihilate the servants of evil. 
It cannot harm the pure of heart, and will turn and strike  casters who are
tainted by evil.

